523
00:42:04,365 --> 00:42:06,492
Kau begitu benci makan denganku?

524
00:42:08,327 --> 00:42:11,247
Alkohol, narkotik, berbohong,
berselingkuh, mesum,

525
00:42:11,330 --> 00:42:12,706
