00:43:43,130 --> 00:43:46,592
Saat aku pertama bertemu denganmu,
aku ingat hari itu.

543
00:43:49,928 --> 00:43:51,138
Di sana…

544
00:43:56,518 --> 00:43:57,978
Di dalam ruangan itu,

545
00:44:03,901 --> 00:44:05,235
kau…

546
00:44:09,406 --> 00:44:10,908
di sisiku.

547
00:44:12,618 --> 00:44:13,827
Kau tersenyum.

548
00:44:17,039 --> 00:44:18,123
Datanglah perlahan…

549
00:44:21,627 --> 00:44:22,961
kepadaku.

550
00:44:37,476 --> 00:44:39,353
<i>Kau memberi tahu Pak Hong?</i>

551
00:44:39,436 --> 00:44:40,687
<i>Kau suka jeruk.</i>

552
00:44:41,271 --> 00:44:43,107
Apa maksudmu? Kenapa Pak Hong?

553
00:44:44,358 --> 00:44:45,901
Dia membawa jeruk.

554
00:44:46,485 --> 00:44:47,986
Jeruk, puisi.

555
00:44:48,821 --> 00:44:50,906
Aku tak suka hadiah semacam itu.

556
00:44:52,407 --> 00:44:54,493
Namun, kau suka tas.

557
00:44:55,160 --> 00:44:58,789
Seharusnya dia masukan jeruk ke tas,
bukan kantong plastik hitam.

558
00:44:59,373 --> 00:45:02,709
